org.apache.ignite.ml.tree.impurity.gini

Class GiniImpurityMeasure

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.tree.impurity.gini.GiniImpurityMeasure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<GiniImpurityMeasure>, ImpurityMeasure<GiniImpurityMeasure>

    public class GiniImpurityMeasure
extends Object
implements ImpurityMeasure<GiniImpurityMeasure>
    Gini impurity measure which is calculated the following way: \-frac{1}{L}\sum_{i=1}^{s}l_i^2 - \frac{1}{R}\sum_{i=s+1}^{n}r_i^2.
